Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ini ketuaan! 100% kutolak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini kau kuampuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi lain kali, akan kubunuh kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunuh aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunuh aku! Bunuh saja aku!
