Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Battle Royale!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rider…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Henshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Henshin!
