Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Magnum…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rider…
