Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, maksudmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shocker mulai bergerak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang dikatakan oleh Tojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Koomori Otoko adalah Kouda Morio,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sepertinya dia punya pengaruh kuat\Ndi industri hiburan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyelenggarakan berbagai acara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di setiap tempat, dia selalu mengubah\Norang-orang menjadi Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepada semua pria yang datang,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Jika kalian menjadi Shocker sekarang,\Nkalian bisa mendapatkan pacar."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Mereka semua idol."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang dia katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara yang kotor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi idol, ya…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tak ada Reiko,\Nmungkin aku akan terpedaya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ini sudah jadi Shocker, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lanjutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bagian terpentingnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Combat Girls akan menggelar konser
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di Tokyo Central Dome akhir pekan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapasitas dome itu 55.000 orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia berencana merekrut\Npasukan tempur secara besar-besaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini data konser yang kudapatkan\Nbersama Yukaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan data ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita bisa mencari jalan masuk\Ndan menghalangi rencana mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus, Mitsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Puji aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuriko…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tackle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yang memanggilnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kudengar Bu Guru\Nsudah mulai mengajar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana lukamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kalian lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau perampok Shocker itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak hal terjadi setelah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin membalaskan dendam bawahanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku ikut melawan Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, Yuriko,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku senang kau sudah sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih penting lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya membahas operasi ini\Ntanpa melibatkan Tackle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kamen Rider Stronger" Episode 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang ikut bertarung\Nsaat Stronger melawan Hebi Onna
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Pasukan Delzer sendirian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ichiyo, jawab!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemudian, di Episode 36,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamen Rider X dan Amazon juga\Ndatang satu per satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di Episode 37…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Riderman datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di Episode 38,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamen Rider Ichigo dan Nigo\Nakhirnya kembali ke Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuh Rider pun berkumpul,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bekerja sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan berjuang mati-matian\Nmelawan Raksasa Batu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Semua Kamen Rider bersaudara."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya terinspirasi\Noleh kata-kata Stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berpegangan tangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengumpulkan tenaga,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mengepung Raksasa Batu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ketujuh Kamen Rider itu\Nmengakhiri pertarungan panjang…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sedang bicara apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi, di sana
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tackle tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ultra Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Tackle Generasi Kedua!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pergi bersama kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Bu Guru adalah\Njuara di kejuaraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak mungkin Bu Guru tidak ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika musuh yang kuat muncul,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa yang Kamen Rider lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita lawan bersama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan mengalahkan Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia muncul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gratis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tumben sekali kau memberi kami gratisan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan pada kalian, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa buang waktu,\Nmari bahas rencananya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum itu, mari kita minum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk merayakan kesembuhan Bu Guru\Ndan berkumpulnya kita semua!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dia lakukan di saat seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ini siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Hakkyoku Hachiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menanyakan namamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, apa yang kau lakukan bersamanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertarung dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bertarung?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Lihat apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa kau dipukul?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cuma manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria ini terus menantangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah menguasai Hakkyoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak itu, dia bertarung di arena\Nbawah tanah sebagai petarung jalanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hingga akhirnya, dia tak terkalahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, untuk memuaskan\Nhati wanita yang dicintainya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia berjuang di medan tempur\Npembuatan ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari tadi kau bicara apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia memang menarik, Koomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah berlatih dengannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mulai paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya manusia punya sesuatu\Nyang disebut semangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang dengan semangat yang pantang goyah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa mengeluarkan kekuatan luar biasa\Ndari dalam diri mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Koomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan remehkan manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tak mau kecewa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebaiknya berhati-hatilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin monster sepertiku\Nkalah dari manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau teman Kumoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau makan ramen bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kubunuh kau, jelek!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah tak tahan hidup sembunyi-sembunyi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di tengah masyarakat manusia lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Semangat"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, semangatku adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kemarahan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian siap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ya.\N- Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu saja, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kukalahkan kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Operasi dimulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdasarkan susunan acara yang kita dapat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Koomori Otoko akan muncul
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pada puncak konser, yaitu acara utama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia akan menggunakan Combat Girls\Ndan penari latar
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mengubah penonton\Nmenjadi pasukan tempur.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuan kita adalah\Nmenghentikan rencana itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, hal terpenting adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keselamatan penonton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi 55.000 orang yang datang\Nmenyaksikan konser ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita harus membuat rencana\Nuntuk mengevakuasi mereka dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan melawan Shocker\Ndilakukan setelahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal cara menyusup masuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yukaris dan Nakao akan menyamar\Nsebagai kontraktor Shocker
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan membawa kita masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kita berhasil masuk dengan aman,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita akan menuju ke lokasi masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak dan Tojima akan bersiaga\Ndi dekat atap dome yang terbuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya pertarungan akan pecah\Nsetelah operasi dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tolong bersiaga di sana\Nsampai ada aba-aba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawan kita adalah Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti akan terjadi hal yang tak terduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika itu terjadi,\Nkita harus menyesuaikan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa isi kotak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembang api yang akan dipakai\Ndi paruh kedua konser.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}merepotkan juga kalau\Nmemesannya mendadak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dengar pesanan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami harus memeriksa kotak itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong beri tahu Tuan Koomori Otoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri tahu kalau pesanan mendadak itu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan menyusahkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau demi\NTuan Koomori Otoko kesayangan kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami akan menyelesaikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudah, sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu si Bos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tak jumpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos tampak muram akhir-akhir ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kami mau mengajak Bos ke konser.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos mau dukung siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga istri sekaligus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos pasti senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masih hidup?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian jadi begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalian masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Bos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Bos ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tempat konser yang diselenggarakan\NTuan Koomori Otoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tuan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos ke sini untuk menggagalkan\Nrencana Shocker, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasukan Tempur Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun yang mengganggu rencana kami\Nakan dilenyapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan membunuhmu.
